1
00:00:01,420 --> 00:00:03,040
Close your eyes.

2
00:00:03,040 --> 00:00:04,170
Why...?

3
00:00:04,170 --> 00:00:07,340
I'm going to trim your eyebrows.
Don't want them getting in your eyes.

4
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:09,930
Oh, right.

5
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:14,260
(Why did my heart just skip a beat...?)

6
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:20,020
Does it hurt?

7
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:21,560
No.

8
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:25,690
(He's so gentle...
And his hands are beautiful.)

9
00:00:25,690 --> 00:00:26,860
What's your major?

10
00:00:26,860 --> 00:00:29,030
Psychology. You?

11
00:00:29,490 --> 00:00:30,990
Computer Science.

12
00:00:30,990 --> 00:00:33,160
By the way, just call me Yuki.

13
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:34,990
Oh.

14
00:00:34,990 --> 00:00:36,910
I'm Makoto.

15
00:00:50,260 --> 00:00:51,510
All done.

16
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:55,390
Who is that?

17
00:00:55,390 --> 00:00:56,470
It's Makoto.

18
00:00:56,470 --> 00:00:58,060
Are you a magician?

19
00:00:58,060 --> 00:00:59,270
(Chuckles)

20
00:00:59,270 --> 00:01:00,600
You're being so dramatic.

21
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:03,860
But look at this! It's incredible...
You really are a magician!

22
00:01:03,860 --> 00:01:05,270
You're getting a little carried away.

23
00:01:05,270 --> 00:01:08,820
This is the first time...
I've ever felt like this.

24
00:01:08,820 --> 00:01:10,990
(I feel like he keeps looking at me...)

25
00:01:10,990 --> 00:01:13,110
(But still...
Why does my heart keep pounding like this?)

26
00:01:13,110 --> 00:01:15,530
Don't look away.

27
00:01:15,530 --> 00:01:17,410
Look at me.
